  "texts": [
    "The dataset contains 6962 instances (rows) of patient admission and 16 features for each instance.",
    "Each row describes the parameters of a patient such as symptoms and some biochemical parameters used to determine the severity level as summarised in Table 3.",
    "Each row also contains the assigned triage level as follows with decrescent level of risk:",
    "• Red: the patient needs immediate attention;",
    "• red: the patient needs intervention in a short time;"
  ]
}